a haughty seraph~
A haughty seraph standing at attention looks down his nose at you.
~
A large, winged being stands at attention before the eastern door.  He is clad
in thick armor but seems to wield no weapon.  Instead, his bony fingers end in
what appear to be very sharp, crystalline spikes.  His stony face betrays no
emotion other than disdain for your presence.  
~
