guardian basalt golem construct~
Guardian basalt golem~
A mountainous construct of basalt towers over you.  His eyes glow with an eerie red light.
~
With a central mass of a square but smooth chunk of basalt, appendages appear
to be better described as 'really close' to the golem, rather than attached to
it.  A rounded, emotionless head floats just barely above the surface of the
torso.  This construct stands squarely before you and the western door.  
~
