#30502
griffin beast maltheus guard~
Maltheus, the foundation's animator~
Maltheus, the foundation's animator, is tinkering with one of the many panels on the wall.
~
Maltheus appears to be very focused on the panels on the wall.  He makes
subtle changes while constantly glancing at the green bars of light in the
room.  Despite his massive frame, he moves gracefully while he is working.  
He appears to be a griffin, but molded somehow to be more humanoid.  Maltheus
still very much looks the part of bird mixed with beast.  There are large
retractable talons embedded in his scaly, yellow arms.  Two muscular wings
almost as tall as him are pulled tightly to his back, appearing almost as a
cape.  
~
