#30503
beast bentham guard golem construct animator~
Bentham, the foundation's animator~
Bentham, the foundation's animator, is pacing back and forth between the panels on the wall.
~
Bentham feverishly watches the bars of light set into the stone.  Every few
moments he makes some adjustments on the nearby panels.  He appears to be a
magical construct of some sort, a golem built of the same materials as the
walls around you.  He appears to be designed for his task, with a short and
spindly frame able to move lithely between the panels despite weight of the
stone.  Though he appears to be magically formed, and therefore controlled,
but his actions betray a sentience not typically found in golems.  
~
